name: Terrence Whitestrand
description:
I love life and I love living life. I enjoy the outdoors, traveling, restaurants, laughing, going to cultural events, and sociaLizing with quality people. Its just better living and sharing life with someone else 🙂
I did my undergrad in Ohio university, and have lived in a few different countries.
I enjoy being active, healthy and staying fit. Family and friends Are important to me as well.
If you’d like to know more Say “hi”. I didn’t reveal a lot about myself for you to read on purpose. Rather we chat, talk, engage in conversation to get to know each other instead of us reading through a long page in this section about each other. Also, just because someone looks like a good match “on paper”, doesn’t necessarily translate in reality.
